      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以主节点是HealthTech_EMR_Sync，然后两个分支分别连向诊断引擎和患者记录系统对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
