      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Nome de Usuário是回到DiagnosticEngine自身，Data de Nascimento连到PatientRecords对吗？还有这个子图命名为Registro可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
